PrecisAmendment to Order in Council P.C. 1986-2042, as amended, that increases, from $5 billion US to $10 billion US, the amount thereby authorized to be raised on U.S. financial markets from time to time by way of the issue and sale of Treasury Bills or Treasury Notes (Canada Bills).
